getbild.com

Bild - Modern Hardware Data Management

Cloud based PDM, storage, project management, and design reviews. See how a cloud-based PDM system can get your engineering team moving faster! If your team is on SolidWorks, GrabCAD, Creo, or another CAD system, Bild can help!

We use it currently. It definitely takes a learning curve but is nice when it works. Compared to grabcad it is nice to have revisions on individual parts but we have had multiple issues with stuff not syncing or where someone cannot edit stuff. I feel like it has gotten a bit better over the course of the season. I dont have any experience with the other services mentioned but I would say it is better than Google drive.

I have the Maker license of Solidworks for personal use and 3DExperience is included. I just use the desktop program and skip 3DE. I save everything on my own cloud service as our FRC team uses Fusion 360 - which I have my own gripes about. Solidworks is still, I think, the best CAD program for mechanical design. I have been using it daily at work for the past 6 years.
